  <aspecttable>DB-HV-1969</aspecttable>
  <name>Combined block + distant signal at short breaking distance</name>
  <reference>See <a href="http://www.sh1.org/eisenbahn/shhp.htm">sh1's page</a> or the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/German_railway_signalling#Home_signal.2Fdistant_signal_.28H.2FV.29">Wikipedia</a></reference>
  <description>Signal to use in blocks, with distant signal head at short breaking distance from next main signal.
  If main signal shows stop (Hp0) then distant signal is dark.</description>
  
  <appearances>

    <appearance>
      <aspectname>Hp0</aspectname>
      <show>red</show>
      <show>dark</show>
      <imagelink type="prototype">../../../resources/icons/largeschematics/aspects/DB-HV-1969/block_distant_short/hp0+dark_short.gif</imagelink>
